Standard
* Undo/Redo
* Save As... (make copy under new name)
* Password recovery via email

Graphics
* Better textures
* Rounding of edges
* Better shadows

Functionality
* Wallpaper
* Doors, windows, entryway
* Physical units (e.g. feet)
* Separate width from length
* Different room shapes (e.g. circular, or corner cut off, etc)
* Add/move light sources, alter softness of light source
* More furniture items
* Additional items (e.g. vases) requiring extra coordinate
* Stairs, rugs, carpets

Visualization
* Collision detection
* Zoom in/out
* Ability to tilt upwards/downwards on camera
* Able to see the light source(s)
